---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects | Enam Amevo" currentPage="projects">
  <div id="projects">
    <h2 class="heading">Technical Engineering Logs</h2>
    <div class="project-grid">

      <div class="project-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="project-card-header">
          <h3>[0x01] Digital Calculator System</h3>
          <span class="card-toggle">&#9654;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-summary">32-bit ripple-carry adder with FSM controller</div>
        <div class="project-card-details">
          <p>Implemented a 32-bit ripple-carry adder with an FSM-based controller, integrating memory and arithmetic logic. Verified timing constraints across 1000+ test cases using Cadence Xcelium and Synopsys Verdi, achieving 50% functional coverage.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">SystemVerilog</span>
            <span class="tag">Cadence</span>
            <span class="tag">Synopsys</span>
            <span class="tag">FSM</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="project-card-header">
          <h3>[0x02] Retrofuturistic DSP Control</h3>
          <span class="card-toggle">&#9654;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-summary">Real-time DSP on XMOS multicore microcontrollers</div>
        <div class="project-card-details">
          <p>Developed real-time DSP control modules for XMOS multicore microcontrollers to manage low-latency USB audio streaming. Implemented run-time coefficient updates for digital filters to allow dynamic audio equalization.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">XMOS</span>
            <span class="tag">DSP</span>
            <span class="tag">Audio</span>
            <span class="tag">Embedded</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="project-card-header">
          <h3>[0x03] FPGA LED Controller</h3>
          <span class="card-toggle">&#9654;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-summary">Logarithmic LUT with 6-bit brightness on DE10 FPGA</div>
        <div class="project-card-details">
          <p>Implemented a logarithmic LUT and 10-bit LED mask with 6-bit brightness control on a DE10 FPGA. Validated design through oscilloscope testing and simulation while leading a 5-person integration team.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">FPGA</span>
            <span class="tag">Verilog</span>
            <span class="tag">DE10</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="project-card-header">
          <h3>[0x04] Plasma & Dielectrics Research</h3>
          <span class="card-toggle">&#9654;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-summary">MOV characterization for high-voltage DC applications</div>
        <div class="project-card-details">
          <p>Fabricated and characterized metal oxide varistor (MOV) samples for high-voltage DC applications. Performed SEM and XRD characterization to correlate material properties with electrical performance.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Materials</span>
            <span class="tag">SEM</span>
            <span class="tag">XRD</span>
            <span class="tag">HV</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
